item.dc:creator: @zerogordo zerogordo
item.description:
@zerogordo wrote:

[quote=“tessa pk, post:5, topic:315300”]dont use hamachi use no-ip.com
alot better[/quote]

Not everyone can port forward and maybe they want it to be private? This section is for helping not giving opinions.

On topic. You can normally change the ports for a source in the Server class. Make sure you have port forwarded your firewall (i don’t recommend turning it off). For hamachi im pretty sure you can use ports 43594 5555. If this is not correct, someone that does know tell me so I can edit.
